{"title":"勇士","authors":["文兵"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别叫我模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也别称我英雄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干脆叫我“兵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人民的子弟兵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问我叫什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说出来可不好听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶名叫“老软”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入伍以后才叫“张勇。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我的家庭历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唉！不问也好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一想起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里就气恼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我小时候家贫难熬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给地主放牛割草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为损坏了一张镰刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主把我开除掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日战争一开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里闹减租减息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家才有了地种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也不饿肚皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年我才十七，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身个不高可有力气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下决心当了八路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在敌后打着游击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从入伍当了兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才开始变聪明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上课懂了好多道理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打仗立了好几次功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一次立功后我入了党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一次冲锋时我负了伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一次打仗我缴获了枪炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些，我都一一记在心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党教我“好好为人民服务！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们永远是战斗队！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些话，我都记在日记本上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我每周看几回，念几回！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拿着向敌人夺来的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担任着国防的前卫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镇压坏蛋们的捣乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备打断侵略者的狗腿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的战友成千成万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的战友个个勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着毛主席和朱德总司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只是“一个”勇敢的战斗员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗员和共产党员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些称号我就挺喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可千万别称我英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也别叫我模范！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于高碑店军次"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}